WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.240
School will start soon.

00:02.760 --> 00:04.600
I’m going to be different this time for sure.

00:05.160 --> 00:09.300
I’m going to be an ordinary, light-hearted junior high school student.

00:10.280 --> 00:13.120
I hope I don’t have many of the same classmates I had in elementary school.

00:13.880 --> 00:16.620
Mom and Dad were talking on the phone.

00:17.120 --> 00:18.980
Were they worried about me?

00:19.460 --> 00:22.720
That’s okay. You can both relax and not worry.

00:23.720 --> 00:26.060
I saw it again for the first time in a long while.

00:26.480 --> 00:28.060
Is it an illusion?

00:28.500 --> 00:32.500
Is there something wrong with my mind?

00:33.360 --> 00:36.440
I don’t care if I’m sick or not.

00:37.840 --> 00:39.580
I just want it to stop.
